Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [Date]

1. Introduction

Welcome to Lan Nansa! Lan Nansa is a mobile application that offers various features designed to assist users with product information, ingredient analysis, AI chat support, and access to humanitarian aid resources. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information. By using the Lan Nansa app, you agree to the terms described in this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

    User Information: When you use our app, we may collect information such as your name, email address, and profile picture.

    Product Search: When you search for product information, we may collect the product names you search for.

    Halal or Haram Checker: When you use the ingredient analysis feature, the images you upload and the results of the analysis may be collected.

    AI Chat Support: Conversations with our AI chatbot may be logged and collected to improve the service.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

    To provide and improve our services, including product search, ingredient analysis, and AI chat support.

    To personalize your experience and provide you with relevant content.

    To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.

    To send you updates and notifications related to the app.

4. Disclosure of Your Information

We may share your information with third parties under the following circumstances:

    With your consent: We may share your information when you give us your explicit permission.

    With our service providers: We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in delivering and improving our services.

    For legal reasons: We may share your information to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property.

5. Security

We take reasonable measures to safeguard your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

6. Children's Privacy

Lan Nansa is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under 13. If you believe that we have unintentionally collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us to have it removed.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective when posted on the app. Your continued use of Lan Nansa after any changes signify your acceptance of those changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [contact email address].
